    <div class="popup" id="popup1">
        <h2>Which Vaccine Will Be Used?</h2>
        <p>A HPV vaccine that protects against 4 types of HPV (6, 11, 16, 18,) called Gardasil 4-Valent HPV vaccine.</p>
        <a href="#" onclick="history.go(-1);"><button>OK</button></a>
